## Key Directories
- **Includes/** - Core plugin functionality
  - **Core/** - Main plugin logic and initialization
  - **Base/** - Abstract classes and base functionality
  - **Controllers/** - Request handling and business logic
  - **Models/** - Data models and database interactions
  - **Services/** - Business services and external integrations
  - **Options/** - Plugin settings and configuration management
  - **Helpers/** - Utility functions and helper classes
  - **Filters/** - WordPress filter hooks and modifications
  - **Widgets/** - Custom WordPress widgets

- **Admin/** - WordPress admin interface
  - **Controllers/** - Admin-specific controllers
  - **Assets/** - CSS, JS, and frontend assets
  - **Views/** - Admin view templates

- **Frontend/** - Public-facing functionality
  - **Controllers/** - Frontend controllers
  - **Filters/** - Frontend-specific filters
  - **Services/** - Frontend services

- **Settings/** - Plugin settings interface
  - **Controllers/** - Settings controllers
  - **Views/** - Settings UI components (React-based)

- **modules/** - Feature modules
  - **wizard/** - Setup wizard
  - **REST/** - REST API endpoints
  - **machine-translation/** - AI translation features
  - **sync/** - Content synchronization
  - **sitemaps/** - Multilingual sitemaps

## Build System
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Node.js dependencies and build scripts
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js) - PostCSS configuration

## Key Constants
- `EASY_WP_TRANSLATOR_VERSION` - Plugin version
- `EASY_WP_TRANSLATOR_FILE` - Main plugin file path
- `EASY_WP_TRANSLATOR_DIR` - Plugin directory path
- `EWT_COOKIE` - Language cookie name
- `EWT_ADMIN` - Whether in admin context
- `EWT_AJAX_ON_FRONT` - Whether AJAX request on frontend
